{"tid":1844904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［馬交］旅局公函限湖北客離澳 否則入住隔離營","createTime":"2020-01-26T23:20:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T03:37:26.000Z","uid":18750,"like":121,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"3d23ec852bb1aed1fa279a14150b8a720cb612fa","tid":1844904,"uid":18750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T23:20:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ku3uUt9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKu3uUt9.jpg&h=78d63a95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【澳門日報消息】網傳旅遊局已向各大酒店發出公函，以防止新型冠狀病毒蔓延酒店場所應採取的緊急措施。<br />\n<br />\n函件中指為防止疫情蔓延，以保障居民及旅客的健康，請貴酒店立即通知所有來自武漢市或湖北省的旅客，1月27日早上9時前離開澳門，如該些旅客不欲離開澳門，則將由澳門特別行政區政府統一安排其入住隔離營。<br />\n<br />\n【更新】澳門旅遊局今日(27日)凌晨回覆本報查詢，證實發出上述通知，以便酒店知會客人，配合政府執行相關工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.modaily.cn/amucsite/web/index.html#/detail/9328069\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.modaily.cn%2Famucsite%2Fweb%2Findex.html%23%2Fdetail%2F9328069&d=0fPPgjUU32Qc%2B%2Bj2t4ropFKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=064f39d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.modaily.cn/amucsite/web/index.html#/detail/9328069</a><br />\n<br />\n香港呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db9f574effefb1d2c957c82e515a24eab11e6c2","tid":1844904,"uid":54511,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T23:24:38.000Z","msg":"老西都唔走啦<br />\n入到去好食好住 好個返湖北<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e7afb3843a7cb0d86126817c478c3963c038684","tid":1844904,"uid":18750,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T23:25:01.000Z","msg":"香港人死香港政府有咩著數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f72644c869faf094129c2aeb10de36733b87d37","tid":1844904,"uid":18750,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"7db9f574effefb1d2c957c82e515a24eab11e6c2","tid":1844904,"uid":54511,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T23:24:38.000Z","msg":